        "message": "Patch Set 10:\n\nUpdated the JIRA and commit message after carefully re-reviewing the spec.\n\nThe new log format looks like this if it can't determine the value of partner name\nChecking Authorization header to determine the value of PartnerName\nChecking X-ONAP-PartnerName header to determine the value of PartnerName\nChecking User-Agent header to determine the value of PartnerName\nChecking X-ClientID header to determine the value of PartnerName\nPartnerName value could not be determined, defaulting partnerName to UNKNOWN.\n\nYou can run the junit locally to see the same.",
